            <title>外媒：特朗普競選顧問通話遭中國黑客攔截，黑客組織「鹽颱風」滲透美國電信公司</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2024/10/28/salt-typhoon/tech-secure/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=salt-typhoon</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2024/10/28/salt-typhoon/tech-secure/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[Pickle Rick]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Mon, 28 Oct 2024 12:00:01 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[資訊保安]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[Salt Typhoon]]>
            </category>
